languages.text: "Ты упала и кричала от боли. Что произошло?"
"You collapsed, screaming in pain. What happened?"
languages.original_text: "Ты упала и кричала от боли. Что произошло?"

traits.locale_text: "You fell down, screaming in pain. What happened?"
"You fell down, screaming in pain. What happened?"
"You collapsed, screaming in pain. What happened?"
"You collapsed, screaming in pain. What happened?"
"You collapsed, screaming in pain. What happened?"

languages.text: “你刚刚瘫倒在地，一直痛苦地尖叫。发生什么事了？”
languages.original_text: "You collapsed, screaming in pain. What happened?"

traits.locale_text: “你刚刚瘫倒在地，一直痛苦地尖叫。发生什么事了？”

languages.text: «Te desplomaste gritando de dolor. ¿Qué ha sucedido?».
languages.original_text: "You collapsed, screaming in pain. What happened?"

traits.locale_text: «Te desplomaste gritando de dolor. ¿Qué ha sucedido?».

languages.text: « Vous vous êtes effondrée en hurlant de douleur. Que s'est-il passé ? »
languages.original_text: "You collapsed, screaming in pain. What happened?"

traits.locale_text: « Vous vous êtes effondrée en hurlant de douleur. Que s'est-il passé ? »

languages.text: "Ihr seid zusammengebrochen, habt geschrien vor Schmerz. Was ist passiert?"
languages.original_text: "You collapsed, screaming in pain. What happened?"

traits.locale_text: "Ihr seid zusammengebrochen, habt geschrien vor Schmerz. Was ist passiert?"

languages.text: 「あなたは痛みで叫びながら倒れた。何が起きたんだ？」
languages.original_text: "You collapsed, screaming in pain. What happened?"

traits.locale_text: 「あなたは痛みで叫びながら倒れた。何が起きたんだ？」

languages.text: "Acı içinde bağırarak yere yığıldın. Ne oldu?"
languages.original_text: "You collapsed, screaming in pain. What happened?"
